            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Diets of the Sympatric Pacific Sheath-Tailed Bat (Emballonura Semicaudata Rotensis) and Mariana Swiftlet (Aerodramus bartsch) on Aguiguan, Mariana Islands",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ernest W.",
                    "lastName": "Valdez"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
